{#
  07_qos.j2 — QoS class-maps and policy-maps
  Static definitions — no dynamic variables.
  Reusable: any Suncor IOS-XE switch template requiring standard QoS policy.
  To customise queue ratios or DSCP markings, edit only this file.
#}
